WEBVTT

00:00:51.840 --> 00:00:53.720
Mr. Mu doesn't want to hear nonsense.

00:00:53.720 --> 00:00:55.200
Then what does he want to hear?

00:00:55.200 --> 00:00:56.160
Sweet talk?

00:00:56.960 --> 00:00:58.220
What are you two doing?

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:04.519
Miss Gu.

00:01:05.280 --> 00:01:06.160
Mr. Mu and I

00:01:06.160 --> 00:01:07.220
were just talking.

00:01:07.560 --> 00:01:08.320
Please don't

00:01:08.320 --> 00:01:09.200
misunderstand.

00:01:09.200 --> 00:01:10.200
Why so nervous?

00:01:11.480 --> 00:01:13.280
Did I say anything about you two?

00:01:17.320 --> 00:01:18.240
Qiushan.

00:01:18.960 --> 00:01:20.400
I trust your judgment.

00:01:20.720 --> 00:01:22.850
