00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:17.360
Jiang Chunyu.

00:10:18.320 --> 00:10:20.180
Don't make trouble for no reason.

00:10:20.240 --> 00:10:21.280
You should know your place

00:10:21.280 --> 00:10:23.340
and what kind of family you come from.

00:10:23.360 --> 00:10:25.240
